{"title":"Save on Bikes & Cycling Gear During the REI Anniversary Sale","link":"https://bikerumor.com/save-on-bikes-amp-cycling-gear-during-the-rei-anniversary-sale/","date":1684799150000,"content":"<p><strong>REI’s biggest sale of the year</strong> is a prime time to save on bikes, saddles, helmets, and other cycling gear. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>We’ve pulled out highlights from Co-op Cycles as well as accessories from top brands like Smith, Bontrager, and more. There are even deals on stationary trainers. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Not everything is on sale, but REI Co-op members can still save. Use coupon code <strong>ANNIV23</strong> at checkout to save 20% on one full-price item and an extra 20% on one REI Outlet item May 19 – 29.</p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspgearbrspreianniversarybiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2F%3Fcm_mmc%3Daff_AL-_-5889-_-7185-_-NA%26avad%3D7185_f30b4d68d\" target=\"_blank\">Shop the REI Anniversary Sale</a>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Co-op Cycle</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspgearbrspreianniversarybiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F189967%2Fco-op-cycles-generation-e11-electric-bike%3Fcm_mmc%3Daff_AL-_-5889-_-7185-_-NA%26avad%3D7185_f30b4eda5\" target=\"_blank\">Co-op Cycles Generation e1.1 &amp; e1.2 Electric Bikes</a></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-Generation-e1.1-e1.2-Electric-Bikes.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"481\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-Generation-e1.1-e1.2-Electric-Bikes-800x481.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-Generation-e1.1-e1.2-Electric-Bikes-800x481.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-Generation-e1.1-e1.2-Electric-Bikes-297x179.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-Generation-e1.1-e1.2-Electric-Bikes-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-Generation-e1.1-e1.2-Electric-Bikes-768x462.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-Generation-e1.1-e1.2-Electric-Bikes-1536x924.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-Generation-e1.1-e1.2-Electric-Bikes-2048x1233.jpg 2048w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo/REI</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Co-op Cycles <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=7185&amp;ctc=gjspreianniversarysalebiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F189967%2Fco-op-cycles-generation-e11-electric-bike\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Generation e1.1 electric bike</strong></a> provides pedal-assist power up to 20 mph. It has a rear cargo rack, a step-through frame, and wide tires for stability over paved and unpaved terrain. It has a range of 30-40 miles with pedal assist.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=7185&amp;ctc=gjspreianniversarysalebiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F190640%2Fco-op-cycles-generation-e12-electric-bike\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Generation e1.2</strong></a> builds off the e1.1’s design but adds a removable front rack and a battery capacity of 672-watt hours for a range of 40-50 miles with pedal assist.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The removable battery comes with a lock to secure it while parked away from home. Other specs include hydraulic brakes, built-in front, and rear lights, and of course, a kickstand.</p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspgearbrspreianniversarybiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F189967%2Fco-op-cycles-generation-e11-electric-bike%3Fcm_mmc%3Daff_AL-_-5889-_-7185-_-NA%26avad%3D7185_f30b4eda5\" target=\"_blank\">Shop e1.1 Now</a>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspgearbrspreianniversarybiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F190640%2Fco-op-cycles-generation-e12-electric-bike%3Fcm_mmc%3Daff_AL-_-5889-_-7185-_-NA%26avad%3D7185_b30b6563d\" target=\"_blank\">Shop e.12 Now</a>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspgearbrspreianniversarybiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F189692%2Fco-op-cycles-cty-21-step-through-bike%3Fcm_mmc%3Daff_AL-_-5889-_-7185-_-NA%26avad%3D7185_e30b4c16d\" target=\"_blank\">Co-op Cycles CTY 2.1 Step-Through Bike</a></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-CTY-2.1-Step-Through-Bike.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"373\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-CTY-2.1-Step-Through-Bike-800x373.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-CTY-2.1-Step-Through-Bike-800x373.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-CTY-2.1-Step-Through-Bike-297x139.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-CTY-2.1-Step-Through-Bike-120x56.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-CTY-2.1-Step-Through-Bike-768x358.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-CTY-2.1-Step-Through-Bike-1536x716.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-CTY-2.1-Step-Through-Bike-2048x955.jpg 2048w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo/REI</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Co-op Cycles CTY 2.1 sports city bike details include a sloped crossbar for stepping over and riser handlebars with wider grips for ergonomics. It’s a 16-speed with a 2 x 8 drivetrain on a Shimano 46/30T crankset and runs a Shimano Altus group. It has an aluminum frame with 700c wheels, disc brakes, and a suspension fork with 63mm of travel.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>There’s room for add-ons, too. The frame has mounts for a bag on the top tube, a water bottle, mounts for fenders, and a rear rack. </p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspgearbrspreianniversarybiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F189692%2Fco-op-cycles-cty-21-step-through-bike%3Fcm_mmc%3Daff_AL-_-5889-_-7185-_-NA%26avad%3D7185_e30b4c16d\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Now</a>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspgearbrspreianniversarybiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F159859%2Fco-op-cycles-adv-22-bike%3Fcm_mmc%3Daff_AL-_-5889-_-7185-_-NA%26avad%3D7185_b30b65e0d\" target=\"_blank\">Co-op Cycles ADV 2.2 Bike</a></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-ADV-2.2-Bike.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"396\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-ADV-2.2-Bike-800x396.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-ADV-2.2-Bike-800x396.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-ADV-2.2-Bike-297x147.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-ADV-2.2-Bike-120x59.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-ADV-2.2-Bike-768x381.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-ADV-2.2-Bike-1536x761.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Co-op-Cycles-ADV-2.2-Bike-2048x1015.jpg 2048w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo/REI</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This 20-speed gravel grinder has an aluminum frame and carbon fork, for a balance of durability and weight savings. It comes equipped with gravel-specific components, including the Shimano GRX 2 x 10 drivetrain and the GRX Shadow Plus rear derailleur, which reduces chain slap and noise on choppy terrain. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The ADV 2.2 also has Tektro mechanical disc brakes 12-degree flared handlebars, and rides atop WTB Nano Comp 700c x 40mm tires with a hybrid tread that’s sleeker in the center and knobby on the edges.</p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspgearbrspreianniversarybiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F159859%2Fco-op-cycles-adv-22-bike%3Fcm_mmc%3Daff_AL-_-5889-_-7185-_-NA%26avad%3D7185_b30b65e0d\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Now</a>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspgearbrspreianniversarybiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F190743%2Fco-op-cycles-rev-20-kids-bike%3Fcm_mmc%3Daff_AL-_-5889-_-7185-_-NA%26avad%3D7185_f30b4e73d\" target=\"_blank\">Co-op Cycles REV 20 Kids’ Bike</a></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/REI-Co-op-Cycles-REV-20-kids-bike.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"442\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/REI-Co-op-Cycles-REV-20-kids-bike-800x442.jpeg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/REI-Co-op-Cycles-REV-20-kids-bike-800x442.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/REI-Co-op-Cycles-REV-20-kids-bike-297x164.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/REI-Co-op-Cycles-REV-20-kids-bike-120x66.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/REI-Co-op-Cycles-REV-20-kids-bike-768x424.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/REI-Co-op-Cycles-REV-20-kids-bike-1536x848.jpeg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/REI-Co-op-Cycles-REV-20-kids-bike-2048x1131.jpeg 2048w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo/REI</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This bike is all about transitions. It comes with two brake systems, which provide young riders the opportunity to graduate to hand brakes while relying on more familiar coaster brakes as a fallback. Similarly, it comes with training wheels which can be removed once your kid is ready for life on two wheels. The aluminum frame makes it lighter for kids to handle and the handlebar is a BMX-style setup.</p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspgearbrspreianniversarybiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F190743%2Fco-op-cycles-rev-20-kids-bike%3Fcm_mmc%3Daff_AL-_-5889-_-7185-_-NA%26avad%3D7185_f30b4e73d\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Now</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Biking Gear</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspgearbrspreianniversarybiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F152860%2Fthousand-chapter-mips-bike-helmet%3Fcm_mmc%3Daff_AL-_-5889-_-7185-_-NA%26avad%3D7185_d30b2e975\" target=\"_blank\">Thousand Chapter MIPS Bike Helmet</a></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Thousand-chapter-mips-bike-helmet.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Thousand-chapter-mips-bike-helmet-800x533.jpeg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Thousand-chapter-mips-bike-helmet-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Thousand-chapter-mips-bike-helmet-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Thousand-chapter-mips-bike-helmet-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Thousand-chapter-mips-bike-helmet-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Thousand-chapter-mips-bike-helmet-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Thousand-chapter-mips-bike-helmet-2048x1366.jpeg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Thousand-chapter-mips-bike-helmet-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo/REI</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This helmet by Thousand has urban styling. It’s complete with a visor and has the in-mold construction and MIPS safety rating you’d want in a road or MTB helmet. It has eight vents to airflow channels, a magnetic chinstrap closure, and a lock channel for securing the helmet together with your bike. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, a 30-lumen magnetic taillight turns on automatically when magnetically attached to the helmet and has a 1-hour runtime (2 hours if flashing).</p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspgearbrspreianniversarybiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F152860%2Fthousand-chapter-mips-bike-helmet%3Fcm_mmc%3Daff_AL-_-5889-_-7185-_-NA%26avad%3D7185_d30b2e975\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Now</a>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspgearbrspreianniversarybiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F172463%2Fergon-smc-sport-gel-saddle-mens%3Fcm_mmc%3Daff_AL-_-5889-_-7185-_-NA%26avad%3D7185_d30b2eb05\" target=\"_blank\">Ergon SMC Sport Gel Saddle — Men’s</a></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Ergon-SMC-Sport-Gel-Saddle-Men_s.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"448\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Ergon-SMC-Sport-Gel-Saddle-Men_s-800x448.jpeg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Ergon-SMC-Sport-Gel-Saddle-Men_s-800x448.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Ergon-SMC-Sport-Gel-Saddle-Men_s-297x166.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Ergon-SMC-Sport-Gel-Saddle-Men_s-120x67.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Ergon-SMC-Sport-Gel-Saddle-Men_s-768x430.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Ergon-SMC-Sport-Gel-Saddle-Men_s-1536x860.jpeg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Ergon-SMC-Sport-Gel-Saddle-Men_s-2048x1147.jpeg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Ergon-SMC-Sport-Gel-Saddle-Men_s-400x225.jpeg 400w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo/REI</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This MTB gel saddle balances relief from pressure with a range of motion. It’s designed with a large contact area, Orthopedic Comfort Foam, and a composite shell built around chromoly rails. (S/M fits sit-bone width of 9–12cm; M/L fits sit-bone width of 12–16cm.)</p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspgearbrspreianniversarybiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F172463%2Fergon-smc-sport-gel-saddle-mens%3Fcm_mmc%3Daff_AL-_-5889-_-7185-_-NA%26avad%3D7185_d30b2eb05\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Now</a>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspgearbrspreianniversarybiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F183539%2Fmaxxis-assegai-f60-3ctexotr-tire%3Fcm_mmc%3Daff_AL-_-5889-_-7185-_-NA%26avad%3D7185_c30b5ef05\" target=\"_blank\">Maxxis Assegai F60 3CT/EXO/TR Tire</a></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Maxxis-Assegai-F60-3CT-EXO-TR-Tire.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"505\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Maxxis-Assegai-F60-3CT-EXO-TR-Tire-800x505.jpeg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Maxxis-Assegai-F60-3CT-EXO-TR-Tire-800x505.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Maxxis-Assegai-F60-3CT-EXO-TR-Tire-297x187.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Maxxis-Assegai-F60-3CT-EXO-TR-Tire-120x76.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Maxxis-Assegai-F60-3CT-EXO-TR-Tire-768x485.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Maxxis-Assegai-F60-3CT-EXO-TR-Tire-1536x969.jpeg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Maxxis-Assegai-F60-3CT-EXO-TR-Tire-2048x1292.jpeg 2048w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo/REI</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Assegai is the signature tire of World Cup champion, Greg Minnaar. It’s a tubeless tire with a tall tread for cutting through loam while still offering traction on roots and rock. Sized for 30-50mm rims, the tires are also bolstered with EXO Protection to resist cuts and scuffs on the sidewalls.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Maxxis uses its 3C MaxxTerra rubber here, which is an intermediate compound. The layout puts firmer knobs on the centerline and softer knobs on the sides. </p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspgearbrspreianniversarybiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F183539%2Fmaxxis-assegai-f60-3ctexotr-tire%3Fcm_mmc%3Daff_AL-_-5889-_-7185-_-NA%26avad%3D7185_c30b5ef05\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Now</a>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspgearbrspreianniversarybiking23&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F851142%2Felectra-townie-7d-step-thru-bike%3Fcm_mmc%3Daff_AL-_-5889-_-7185-_-NA%26avad%3D7185_a30b63849\" target=\"_blank\">Electra Townie 7D Step-Through Bike</a></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Electra-Townie-7D-Step-Through-Bike.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"440\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Electra-Townie-7D-Step-Through-Bike-800x440.jpeg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Electra-Townie-7D-Step-Through-Bike-800x440.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Electra-Townie-7D-Step-Through-Bike-297x163.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Electra-Townie-7D-Step-Through-Bike-120x66.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Electra-Townie-7D-Step-Through-Bike-768x422.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Electra-Townie-7D-Step-Through-Bike-1536x845.jpeg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Electra-Townie-7D-Step-Through-Bike-2048x1126.jpeg 2048w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo/REI</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Made with comfort in mind, this Electra